abstract: Michigan State University is in the chase for the Big Ten title, but will be playing against undefeated Wisconsin without star defensive end William Gholston.
snippet: Michigan State University is in the chase for the Big Ten title, but will be playing against undefeated Wisconsin without star defensive end William Gholston.
lead_paragraph: Michigan State might have beaten rival Michigan rather easily last Saturday in East Lansing, but the reverberations from the game are far from over.

headline.main: Michigan State to Face Wisconsin Without Gholston
